data.description: Set on a double lot totaling 0.51 acres, this charming cape cod in CV schools has 3 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. Most of the home was recently painted including the trim. The first floor includes a large foyer area, living room, kitchen, full bath and two bedrooms each with a ceiling fan. The refrigerator and dishwasher are included in the sale and both were purchased new in 2023. Stove is only 2 years old. To combat hard water, owners installed a water softener. The second floor is comprised of a large bedroom, half bath and bonus room. The unfinished basement houses the laundry area, plenty of storage and a wood burning fireplace. Gym equipment is negotiable.
